{"tid":1002352,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"公平咩？𠵱個世界公平咩？","createTime":"2019-01-31T01:08:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-31T01:15:20.000Z","uid":125976,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"3e29d597951668acb71a4b82fec0c27e9c8da4d5","tid":1002352,"uid":125976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T01:08:57.000Z","msg":"唔公平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n非常之唔公平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以有啲人選擇去自殺未必因為佢廢，可能喺嗰一刻佢哋已經做咗一件最正確同最合乎成本效益嘅事<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n新年前，為今年一眾選擇咗自殺嘅香港人默哀一分鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n因為冇人知將來下一個選擇跳落去嘅人係咪你<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"baff2c4cd96469cd958ae377a3998b996ca47c1f","tid":1002352,"uid":32577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T01:10:49.000Z","msg":"怕痛，不了"},{"pid":"c9bd035a4da6dbdde9d49d0f3ae63c16d066c936","tid":1002352,"uid":125976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"baff2c4cd96469cd958ae377a3998b996ca47c1f","tid":1002352,"uid":32577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T01:10:49.000Z","msg":"怕痛，不了"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T01:13:12.000Z","msg":"咁你繼續喺香港做撚狗啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">如果你冇出生的話</span>"},{"pid":"df47ac9a8206bbf3e77399ca5a944b92cd80d9c9","tid":1002352,"uid":78429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T01:15:20.000Z","msg":"講得啱<br />\n呢個世界咁唔公平，萬一跳樓跌唔死真係好柒"}]}